description: Trystan Bull has been going to his particular gym for over a year now. He's gotten pretty good with the weights, pretty good with his endurance and cardio, but the area he is excelling at is in the cage hitting the bag. He has actually become quite a natural with his hands. Kyle Quinn is new to the gym, but he recognizes talent when he sees it, which is why he's had his eye on Trystan now for some time. Watch as the two of them spar, shadowbox and sweat together. And then watch as they wind down together from their workout. It turns out Kyle is quite a natural with his hands too. And his mouth... and his ass...Enjoy!
title: Raging Bull
